products.name: Filofax Personal Organizer
products.description: Plan your days and schedule with this classic leather organizer. Includes weekly pages, note sections, and pockets for cards and receipts. Stay organized and stylish throughout your busy day.

products.name: Atomic Habits by James Clear
products.description: Learn the tiny behaviors that can lead to remarkable results. James Clear's Atomic Habits reveals practical strategies for improving your life - one small step at a time. Achieve your goals, break bad habits, and build good ones with this insightful and actionable guide.

products.name: Nespresso VertuoPlus Coffee & Espresso Machine
products.description: Enjoy barista-quality coffee at home with this sleek and convenient machine. It brews both classic and espresso coffees with the simple press of a button.

products.name: BenQ GV30 Portable Projector
products.description: Bring the big screen experience anywhere with this compact and versatile projector. Enjoy movies, games, and more with bright, crisp visuals. Durable design and built-in battery make it perfect for outdoor adventures.

products.name: Acer Aspire 5
products.description: Affordable laptop with a 10th Gen Xntel Core i5 processor, enough power for everyday tasks, a long-lasting battery, and a lightweight design.

products.name: Bosch Icon Wiper Blades (Pair)
products.description: Experience superior all-weather performance with these premium wiper blades. Featuring a patented beam design and advanced rubber compound, they offer exceptional clearing in rain, snow, and sleet.

products.name: Sony PlayStation 5
products.description: Experience next-generation gaming with the PlayStation 5 console, boasting ultra-fast loading times, stunning visuals, and immersive 3D audio.

products.name: Nova X7 Pro
products.description: Capture stunning moments with the triple-lens camera system, enjoy immersive entertainment on the vibrant AMOLED display, and stay productive with the powerful Snapdragon 8 Gen 1 processor. Crafted from sleek, durable glass and metal.

products.name: Cuisinart Compact Air Fryer
products.description: Make healthy and delicious meals quickly and easily with this air fryer. Features multiple cooking presets, digital controls, and easy cleanup.

products.name: GoPro HERO10 Black Action Camera
products.description: Capture your most epic adventures with this versatile action camera. Shoot stunning 5.3K video, ultra-smooth 240fps slow-motion, and high-resolution photos, all while remaining waterproof and durable.

products.name: Nintendo Switch OLED Model
products.description: Enjoy vibrant colors and improved contrast on the Switch OLED's larger screen, perfect for both handheld and docked play. Explore dozens of exclusive games and classic franchises alike.

products.name: Wilson Pro Staff Team V13.0 Tennis Racquet
products.description: Unleash your inner Federer with this lightweight and powerful racquet. Featuring a large sweet spot and stiff flex, it offers control and precision for players of all levels.

products.name: GoPro HERO10 Black
products.description: Versatile action camera. High-resolution video, stabilization technology.

products.name: Logitech G502 Lightspeed Wireless Gaming Mouse
products.description: Dominate the competition with the G502 Lightspeed, featuring a customizable DPI sensor, 11 programmable buttons, and ultra-fast wireless connectivity.

products.name: Cuisinart Food Processor
products.description: This powerful food processor makes chopping, grating, and puréeing a breeze. It comes with multiple attachments for different tasks, making it a versatile kitchen tool.

products.name: Spalding NBA Team Backpack
products.description: Show off your team spirit with this stylish and functional backpack. Featuring ample storage space for all your training essentials, a comfortable and adjustable design, and your favorite team's logo, it's the perfect companion for the court or gym.

products.name: Black Diamond Spot Headlamp
products.description: Compact and powerful headlamp. Multiple brightness settings, adjustable angle.

products.name: Patagonia Down Sweater Hoody
products.description: Lightweight jacket with water-resistant shell, 800-fill-power down insulation

products.name: Stanley FatMax Xtreme Folding Toolbox
products.description: Keep your tools organized and easily accessible with this durable toolbox. Featuring a spacious interior with removable compartments, a folding handle, and weatherproof construction, it's perfect for job sites and the garage.

products.name: Apple MacBook Air M2
products.description: Sleek and stylish laptop with Apple's M2 chip for incredible performance and efficiency, a beautiful Retina display, and all-day battery life.

products.name: REI Co-op Camp Dome Tent
products.description: Spacious and easy-to-pitch tent. Durable construction, weather-resistant design.

products.name: Corsair K70 RGB MK.2 Low Profile Mechanical Keyboard
products.description: Upgrade your setup with the K70's low-profile Cherry MX mechanical switches, vibrant RGB lighting, and durable aluminum construction.

products.name: Humanscale Freedom Headrest Chair
products.description: Elevate your workspace with this ergonomic chair featuring adjustable lumbar support, a pivoting headrest, and breathable mesh fabric. Stay comfortable and productive throughout the workday.

products.name: CeraVe Daily Facial Moisturizing Lotion
products.description: This fragrance-free, non-comedogenic lotion provides lightweight hydration for normal to dry skin. Formulated with hyaluronic acid and ceramides to lock in moisture and restore the skin barrier.
products.material: Water, glycerin, dimethicone, niacinamide, hyaluronic acid, ceramides

products.name: REN Clean Skincare Ready Steady Glow Daily AHA Tonic
products.description: This gentle exfoliating toner removes dead skin cells, brightens the complexion, and promotes a healthy glow. Suitable for most skin types, except for sensitive skin.
products.material: Aqua (Water), Lactic Acid, Glycolic Acid, Willow Bark Extract, Glycerin, Aloe Vera, Panthenol

products.name: Osprey Daypack
products.description: Versatile daypack. Comfortable straps, organized compartments, hydration sleeve.

products.name: Hydro Flask Trail Series Water Bottle
products.description: Durable and insulated water bottle. Leak-proof lid, easy-to-carry handle.

products.name: Roland FP-30 Digital Piano
products.description: Elevate your practice or performances with this sleek and versatile digital piano. Authentic acoustic piano sounds, weighted keys, and advanced features provide a rich playing experience.

products.name: The New Yorker magazine
products.description: Delve into thought-provoking essays, witty cartoons, and insightful reporting on politics, culture, and current events. The New Yorker's iconic cartoons and sharp writing offer a unique perspective on the world around you.

products.name: Redmi Note 12 Pro Max
products.description: Capture professional-grade photos with the 108MP quad-camera system, experience hyper-smooth performance with the MediaTek Dimensity 1200 chip, and enjoy all-day battery life. Sleek glass and metal design exudes style and durability.

products.name: HP Spectre x360 14
products.description: Convertible laptop with a versatile 360-degree hinge, vibrant OLED touchscreen, powerful Xntel Core i7 processor, and long battery life.

products.name: ASUS ROG Strix G15
products.description: Gaming laptop with a powerful NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3070 graphics card, a high-refresh-rate display for smooth gameplay, and a durable aluminum chassis.

products.name: Jabra Elite 7 Active Earbuds
products.description: Get active without sacrificing sound quality. These sweatproof earbuds deliver powerful audio and secure fit for workouts and everyday adventures. Long-lasting battery and active noise cancellation keep you focused on your goals.
